<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FOSR · Inala Financial Diagnostics</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* ADDING TO YOUR EXISTING STYLES */
        :root {
            --navy: #0E1B2E; --forest: #152E20; --copper: #B5662E; --paper: #F7F3EE;
        }
        .sector-grid, .pricing-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: #fff; padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid #D6CFC5; border-radius: 4px; transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--copper); }
        .price-tag { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond'; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--copper); margin: 1rem 0; }
        .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: var(--forest); color: white; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">FOSR</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#solutions">Solutions</a>
            <a href="#pricing">Engagement Models</a>
            <a href="onboarding.html">Onboarding</a>
            <a href="compliance.html" style="color: var(--copper); font-weight: 600;">Partner Compliance</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section id="solutions" style="background: var(--paper);">
    <div class="container">
        <span class="pill">Who We Serve</span>
        <h2>Institutional Solutions</h2>
        <div class="sector-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Academic & GS 10k</h3>
                <p>Bridge the 'Knowledge-Behavior Gap'. Sequence your curriculum based on structural readiness to ensure higher completion rates and sophisticated impact data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Accelerators</h3>
                <p>Go beyond the pitch deck. Identify behavioral flags like Pricing Uncertainty or Collections Avoidance before you deploy mentors or capital.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>ESD Programmes</h3>
                <p>De-risk your supply chain. Measure the structural reliability of SMME partners to provide targeted Technical Assistance where it matters most.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Lenders & DFIs</h3>
                <p>Reduce cost-to-serve and default risk. Use FOSR as a pre-disbursement audit to pinpoint the exact cause of financial distress in applicants.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
        <span class="pill">Pilot Ready</span>
        <h2>Engagement Models</h2>
        <p>Transparent pricing designed for institutional scalability.</p>
        
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="pill" style="background:#B5662E;">Recommended</div>
                <h3>Institutional Pilot</h3>
                <div class="price-tag">R15,000 <span style="font-size: 1rem; color: #58524A;">once-off</span></div>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; line-height: 2;">
                    <li>✓ Custom Cohort Dashboard</li>
                    <li>✓ Curriculum Mapping (GS 10k)</li>
                    <li>✓ API Integration (SheetDB)</li>
                    <li>✓ Faculty Technical Onboarding</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Assessment Tier</h3>
                <div class="price-tag">R3,500 <span style="font-size: 1rem; color: #58524A;">per founder</span></div>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; line-height: 2;">
                    <li>✓ Intake & Exit Assessment</li>
                    <li>✓ Automated Structural Profile</li>
                    <li>✓ Instant PDF Delivery</li>
                    <li>✓ Longitidunal Impact Data</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer style="background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); padding: 4rem 2rem;">
    <div class="container" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
        <div>
            <p>© 2026 Inala Advisory (Pty) Ltd</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7;">POPIA Compliant · South Africa Based</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="compliance.html" style="color: var(--white); margin-left: 20px;">Compliance Portal</a>
            <a href="onboarding.html" style="color: var(--white); margin-left: 20px;">Partner Onboarding</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
